      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Topple</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Klein_Bottle_Parametrized_5.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/14/Klein_Bottle_Parametrized_5.png/330px-Klein_Bottle_Parametrized_5.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"205\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/14/Klein_Bottle_Parametrized_5.png/500px-Klein_Bottle_Parametrized_5.png 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/14/Klein_Bottle_Parametrized_5.png/960px-Klein_Bottle_Parametrized_5.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Klein_Bottle_Parametrized_5.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Toppled Klein Bottle <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Topple</b>, (ToppleChess)<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> by <a href=\"/Vincent_Tang\" title=\"Vincent Tang\">Vincent Tang</a>, written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a>, first released in June 2018 under the <a href=\"/Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology#License\" title=\"Massachusetts Institute of Technology\">MIT License</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Features\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Features</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Board_Representation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Board Representation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Search\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Evaluation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Evaluation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2018_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2018 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#Misc_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Features\">Features</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Topple&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Features\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Board_Representation\"><a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Topple&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Board Representation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Bitboard_Board-Definition\" title=\"Bitboard Board-Definition\">Bitboard Board-Definition</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/8x8_Board\" title=\"8x8 Board\">8x8 Board</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards#Fancy\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Fancy Magic Bitboards</a> by <a href=\"/Pradu_Kannan\" title=\"Pradu Kannan\">Pradyumna Kannan</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search\"><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Topple&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Search\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a> using <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Threads</a>  <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Shared_Hash_Table\" title=\"Shared Hash Table\">Shared Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table#Bucket\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Four Buckets</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Zobrist_Hashing\" title=\"Zobrist Hashing\">Zobrist Hashing</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">Selectivity</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Check_Extensions\" title=\"Check Extensions\">Check Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/PV_Extensions\" title=\"PV Extensions\">PV Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Singular_Extensions#RestrictedSE\" title=\"Singular Extensions\">Restricted Singular Extensions</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">Pruning</a>/<a href=\"/Reductions\" title=\"Reductions\">Reductions</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Delta_Pruning\" title=\"Delta Pruning\">Delta Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Leaf_Pruning\" title=\"History Leaf Pruning\">History Leaf Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mate_Distance_Pruning\" title=\"Mate Distance Pruning\">Mate Distance Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation Pruning</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Move_Generation#Staged\" title=\"Move Generation\">Staged Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hash_Move\" title=\"Hash Move\">Hash Move</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Killer_Heuristic\" title=\"Killer Heuristic\">Killer Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Evaluation\"><a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Topple&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Evaluation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">Mobility</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">Pawn Structure</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">Pawn Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Topple&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Topple&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2018_...\">2018 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Topple&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2018 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67685\">Topple</a> by <a href=\"/Vincent_Tang\" title=\"Vincent Tang\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 09, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67998\">Topple v0.2.1 Release</a> by <a href=\"/Vincent_Tang\" title=\"Vincent Tang\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 16, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69532\">Automated tuning... finally... (Topple v0.3.0)</a> by <a href=\"/Vincent_Tang\" title=\"Vincent Tang\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 08, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69734\">Topple v0.3.4 released</a> by <a href=\"/Vincent_Tang\" title=\"Vincent Tang\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 26, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69818\">Topple 0.3.5</a> by <a href=\"/Vincent_Tang\" title=\"Vincent Tang\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=70394\">Topple 0.5.0</a> by <a href=\"/Vincent_Tang\" title=\"Vincent Tang\">Vincent Tang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 02, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69754&amp;start=451\">Re: New engine releases 2019</a> by <a href=\"/G%C3%BCnther_Simon\" ti